  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK693">
<l>pōṟṟi ṉariyavai pōṟṟal kaṭuttapiṉ</l>
<l>ṟēṟṟutal yārkku maritu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Ministers who would save themselves should avoid (the commission of) serious errors for if the king's suspicion is once roused, no one can remove it.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
